## Key Conclusion (One Sentence)

> **LibreCAD is an open-source 2D CAD tool,  
not a professional Windows CAD solution.**

The problems encountered are **tool limitations, not skill issues**.

---

## Practical Recommendations

- LibreCAD (Windows): âŒ Avoid
- QCAD Community Edition: âœ… Simple edits / reference
- AutoCAD / BricsCAD: âœ… Collaboration & delivery
- LibreCAD on Linux: Learning / experimentation only

